00:03:13,820 --> 00:03:15,820
is the intensity of certain fears

78
00:03:15,820 --> 00:03:17,820
as reported in the media.

79
00:03:17,820 --> 00:03:19,820
Let me point them out.

80
00:03:19,820 --> 00:03:23,820
